ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to clarify that accredited diplomats and officials, members of visiting forces, certain family members, and persons invited by the Canadian goverment to attend specific meetings should not be subject to either a Temporary Resident Visa fee or a Temporary Resident Permit fee.
